data.title: Reducing Ocean Plastic by 50,000 Tons Annually
data.description: Our biodegradable packaging solutions have prevented 50,000 tons of plastic waste from entering oceans each year.
data.stats: 50,000 tons plastic waste prevented, 2.5M marine animals protected, 15 coastal communities benefited
